<p>🇮🇹 From fragmented <a href="https://tech.eu/2026/04/02/from-fragmented-funding-to-growing-maturity-the-italian-tech-ecosystem/" target="_blank">funding</a> to growing maturity: the Italian tech ecosystem</p>
